Create workspace
  npm init -w api/user-service 

Dependency management:
  To access type written inside shared package

  package.json (Root level):
    "workspaces": [
      "api/auth-service",
      "api/user-service",
      "shared"
    ]
    Tells npm to treat each package as individual project
    Reason for installing packages inside node_modules

    tsconfig.json (Package level)
    "dependencies": {
      "shared": "1.0.0"
    }
    Tells npm that give package is necessary to install in order to execute this package 

  
  
